Date: 2/11/25
Title: Lab 6

1. run oracle virtualbox
2. select expert mode and open settings of tools
3. go to network -> host only network -> create network called vboxnet()
4. edit properties -> DHCP server -> enable server -> apply
5. go back to virtual box and go to file -> import appliance
6. set source to local file system and file to "/local/Vbox/minix3-1-7.ova"
7. expand settings and set MAC Address Policy -> Generate new MAC address for all network adapters -> finish
8. start VM and press 2 to go to custom launch
9. type "root" into login
10. type "passwd" and enter a password
11. type ifconfig to get ip address for later
12. type "tcpd ftp in.ftpd &"
13. go to file directory of host pc and go to "other locations" 
14. connect to server with "ftp://<IP from above>"
15. edit files with emacs
16. go back to VM and cd /usr/src to be able to run make world to update changes
17. use commands "shutdown" then "exit" and then press 2 to go to custom
